    "description": "本課程將引導學生解析、組成、以及運用多樣的流行音樂和聲變化，讓學生以樂器獨奏或合奏方式，實際感受聲響結果，進而培養流行音樂和聲進行之概念。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.常用的和弦進行模式<br>2.基礎三和弦七和弦與原位引伸和弦<br>3.指標性音符 Guide Tones 與和聲音程<br>4.和弦轉位表示法<br>5.調性級數和弦 Diatonic Chords<br>6.老套線條和聲 Line Cliché Voicings<br>7.左手貝殼外型和聲<br>8.無根音引伸和聲<br>9.雙手和聲<br>10.複合多和弦<br>11.板音和聲<br>12.調式化和聲 Modal Voicings<br>13.變化屬和弦<br>14.代理和弦<br>15.調式互換之和弦借用",
        "en": "1.The commonly used chord mode<br>2.Basic triads &amp; seventh and extension chords<br>3.Indicator notes Guide Tones and harmony process<br>4.Chord transposition representation<br>5.Tonal series chords Diatonic Chords<br>6.Sounds Line Cliché Voicings<br>7.Left hand shell appearance harmony<br>8.No root extension and harmony<br>9.Two hands harmony<br>10.Compound multiple chords<br>11.sounds voicings<br>12.Modal Voicings<br>13.Alter dominants chords<br>14.Substitute chords<br>15.Modal interchang"
